--------------------- Deployment -----------------------

. Deployment is a configuration of a desired state. 
. Means we say that on kubenetes cluster we need to 2 replica of java-namespace and if by chance 1 from the 2 containers is crashed so scheduler will provisioned the another pod in that particualr namespace.  

. Service Proxy has an address of the deployment.

Users --->> Service Proxy --->> Deployement.

IMPORTANT :- 
- Everything in k8s is a manifest file. Even if u want to make the cluster, namespace or pods.


